				<text><![CDATA[16. <b>“INDEX / BASE RATEor PRIME LENDING RATE”</b>means the rate of interest fixed by the Company from time to time as its Index rate or Prime Lending Rate. Company has a right to change Index rate or Prime Lending rate based on its internal factors and the same will be notified to the Borrower/s accordingly.<br>
17. <b>“ADDITIONAL INTEREST”</b> means interest levied by Company on delay in payment of the EMI or any other amounts due and payable by the Borrower to the Company.<br>
18. <b>“RESET PERIOD”</b> means Monthly or Bi -Monthly or Quarterly or Half yearly during which the Index rate or Primer lending rate is changed.<br><br>
<b>1. Terms and Conditions:</b><br><br>
<b>1.1</b> The Company may, subject to the Borrower agreeing to the covenants and undertakings as pertaining to the Loan and based on the details provided in the Application made by the Borrower for the said Loan and subject to the terms and conditions in the Loan Agreement, Loan Approval Letter and based on other documents executed or tendered by the Borrower in relation to the said Loan, l end to the Borrower the said Loan.<br>
<b>1.2</b> The relationship between the Company and the Borrower about the Loan shall commence from the date of the Loan Agreement and subsist until all month due and payable by the Borrower to the Company under the Loan Agreement and under all other documents pursuant thereto shall have been fully paid to and received by the Company.<br>
<b>1.3</b> The Loan will be utilized for the purpose for which it is sanctioned as per the Loan Approval Letter and granted as per the Loan Agreement based on the information provided by the Borrower/s in the Application Form / Project Report. Purpose of the Loan shall not be changed in any manner during the Loan and any such change in Purpose shall take place only with the prior written permission of the Company. The Borrower will provide to the Company all the necessary documents as may be required by the Company. The Company shall have the right to appoint auditors to certify the end use of the Loan.<br>
<b>1.4</b> The Loan will be repaid by the Borrower/s by way of EMIs and at the rate of interest arrived in accordance with the terms and conditions in this Agreement and the Schedule annexed hereto. The Borrower shall also pay such processing fees, other costs, charges and expenses as detailed hereinafter. Each EMI shall be calculated based on the monthly rests. The company has right to revise interest rate depending on prevailing market rate, if borrower agreed upon for Floating Rate of Interest.<br>
<b>1.5</b> Time is of the essence of the contract.<br>
